{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build your empire:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build up new cities with strong economies to keep citizens happy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and military resolve to keep them safe from invading forces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/SteamBuildingMid20.gif?t=1737295919\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find new races across Avandalair:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From friendly settlements willing to trade and work together,<br>to settlements ruled by warlords, beast races or world conquering hiveminds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you wage war or make alliances?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/SteamCombatMid20.gif?t=1737295919\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Avandalair's world: </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover old world technology to unlock new weapons, upgrades and city improvements<strong>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/SteamWeaponsMid20.gif?t=1737295919\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Discover new races, friend or foe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Discover new lands to populate with new settlements.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Building</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Build your cities in unique locations.<br>-Connect cities by trade routes and manage various things <br>\u00a0 to keep the population happy.<br>-Raise defensive structures and armies to protect your cities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combat</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Combat your enemies with various unique upgradable weapons.<br>-Raise armies to defend your cities and assault others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Use vehicles and tamable mounts on land, water and air to travel and fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Fight epic bosses that will test your resolve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Skill trees:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Unlock skills and abilities in unique skill trees.<br>-Upgrade weapons and equipment like the placeable turret.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737295919","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/page.bg.jpg?t=1737295919","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/de272a13f16710b6f800525e8768507dbdef6217/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737295919","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/de272a13f16710b6f800525e8768507dbdef6217/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737295919","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build your empire:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build up new cities with strong economies to keep citizens happy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and military resolve to keep them safe from invading forces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/SteamBuildingMid20.gif?t=1737295919\" /></p><p class=\"bb_par